@spec mm_reindex_if_stale_spec  src=tests/specs/mm_reindex_if_stale_spec.lua  loc=50  sha=07eac20  cases=2
@exercises midiManager (h.mm)
@surface   mm:events, mm:reindexIfStale, mm:notes, mm:tokenOf, mm:modify, mm:delete
@harness   bareMM

# Intent
  Phase C pin - design/deferred-reindex.md item 5. mm:reindexIfStale() is the
  scaffold Phase D flips onto: it runs a reindex only when a deferred modify
  left the arrays stale. Nothing sets the stale flag yet, so today the call
  verifiably reindexes nothing - loadIndex gained it at its head as a no-op.

# Helpers
  @fn tokPpqs(mm)  @ 8-12

# Cases
  @case 'reindexIfStale() is a no-op on already-compact state'  [harness]  @ 16-30
  @case 'reindexIfStale() stays inert after a compacting modify'  [harness]  @ 34-48

# Uses (outbound edges)
  @use call midiManager.events  @ 10
  @use call midiManager.reindexIfStale  @ 28,46
  @use call midiManager.notes  @ 42
  @use call midiManager.tokenOf  @ 42
